#문제 2
#페이지 생성 함수수
def pg(num):
  if num==1:
    return num
  elif num==0:
    return num+1
  else:
    return (num-1)*10+1

  

    

    

    

      

      

      

        

        

      

    

             

           

    

      

        
        

          
        

      

    
#url 생성함수
def create_url(search,start,end):
  url_list = []
  for i in range(start,end+1):
    page = pg(i)
    url = 'https://search.naver.com/search.naver?where=news&sm=tab_pge&query='+search+'&sort=0&photo=0&field=0&pd=0&ds=&de=&cluster_rank=138&mynews=0&office_type=0&office_section_code=0&news_office_checked=&nso=so:r,p:all,a:all&start='+str(page)
    url_list.append(url)
  return url_list

#크롤러
def crawler(url,i):
  #i is startpage
  response = requests.get(url)
  html=response.text
  soup=BeautifulSoup(html,'html.parser')
  ul=soup.select_one('ul.list_news')
  news_areas = ul.select('li > div > div')
  crawling_df=pd.DataFrame()
  for news_area in news_areas:
    day=news_area.find_all('span',class_='info')
    if len(day)==2:
      day = list(day[1])
    else:
      day= list(day[0])
    press=news_area.find(class_='info press').text.strip()
    if '언론사 선정' in press:
      press=press[:-6]
    title=news_area.find(class_='news_tit')['title']
    url=news_area.find(class_='news_tit')['href']
    df_list=[i,day[0],press,title,url]
    crawling_df = crawling_df.append(pd.Series(df_list), ignore_index=True)
  return crawling_df
Enter to Rename, Shift+Enter to Preview

  

    

    

    

      

      

      

        

        

      

    

             

           

    

      

        
        

          
        

      

    
#크롤러 동작 함수
def start_crawling():
  final_df=pd.DataFrame()
  print('검색어를 입력하시면 네이버뉴스 기사 정보를 크롤링합니다.')
  search = input('검색어를 입력하세요. : ')
  start = int(input('시작 페이지를 입력하세요 : '))
  end = int(input('종료 페이지를 입력하세요 : '))
  url_list = create_url(search,start,end)
  i=start
  for url in url_list:
    df = crawler(url,i)
    i+=1
    final_df = pd.concat([final_df,df])
  final_df.columns=['page','date','press','title','url']
  print('크롤링 결과를 데이터프레임으로 생성하였습니다.')
  return final_df
